Exclusion criteria

(1) The article addresses a shared PI system OR people's social PI practice;

(1) Works neither address a shared PI system nor include social PI practices;

(2) The use scenario of the system concerns at least two people;

(2) Sharing is not the main purpose/practice of the system;

(3) Sharing is (part of) the purpose of the system;

(3) Doctoral consortium, workshop, panel, opening keynote, courses, commentary; (4) The article was published from Jan. 2010 to Sep. 2023;

(4) Works in progress and mock-ups;

(5) The article is written in English.

